data.description: Welcome home! Step into this beautiful single-story home that that boasts a timeless design.  As you enter, enjoy the charm of the high, wood beam ceilings of this move-in ready home. A fireplace in the main living area provides a warm and comfortable atmosphere.  This well-maintained residence spares no detail providing a seamless transition for its new owners. The absence of carpet throughout the home not only enhances its aesthetic appeal but also ensures ease of maintenance and a clean living environment.  The generous lot surrounding the property provides ample space for entertaining, gardening, building or simply enjoying more privacy.   Hurry! This won't last!
